<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="married-adj">married <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mærid/    美 /'mærid/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>已婚的；有配偶的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please state whether you are single, married, or divorced in the form.
请在表格中注明您是单身、已婚还是离异。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>How do you like married life? 
你认为婚后的生活怎样？</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-married-to">be married to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[表示状态] 与…结婚：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They have been married to each other for 20 years. 
他们已经结婚20年了。</p></div>

<h3 id="get-married-to">get married to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[表示动作] 与…结婚：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Jane got married to her husband immediately after graduation. 
简一毕业就嫁给了她丈夫。</p></div></div>